---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Enterprise Services — Starling AIX" description="Starling builds organizational intelligence systems — then makes sure someone in your organization can run them. Every engagement ends with a person, not a report.">

<!-- ── Hero ──────────────────────────────────────────────────── -->
<section style="position:relative;overflow:hidden;padding:6rem 0 5rem;text-align:center;" class="grid-bg">
  <div class="hero-glow"></div>
  <div class="container" style="position:relative;z-index:1;">

    <div class="badge fade-up" data-delay="0" style="margin-bottom:1.5rem;">
      Enterprise Services
    </div>

    <h1 class="heading-display fade-up" data-delay="0.08"
        style="font-size:clamp(3rem,8vw,5.5rem);margin:0 0 1.5rem;max-width:700px;margin-inline:auto;">
      We build it. We teach it. We <em>staff</em> it.
    </h1>

    <p class="fade-up" data-delay="0.15"
       style="font-size:1.05rem;color:#71717a;line-height:1.75;max-width:540px;margin:0 auto 2.5rem;">
      Starling builds organizational intelligence systems — then makes sure someone in your organization can run them. Every engagement ends with a person, not a report.
    </p>

    <div class="fade-up" data-delay="0.22" style="display:flex;gap:1rem;flex-wrap:wrap;justify-content:center;">
      <a href="https://calendly.com/starlingaix" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="btn btn-primary" style="font-size:0.95rem;padding:0.7rem 1.75rem;">
        Book a Discovery Call
      </a>
      <a href="#how-we-work" class="btn btn-ghost" style="font-size:0.95rem;padding:0.7rem 1.75rem;">
        See How We Work
      </a>
    </div>

  </div>
</section>

<div class="divider"></div>

<!-- ── The Mach 1 Problem ─────────────────────────────────────── -->
<section style="padding:5rem 0;">
  <div class="container">
    <div style="max-width:820px;margin-inline:auto;">
      <p class="section-label fade-up" data-delay="0" style="margin-bottom:0.75rem;">The Mach 1 Problem</p>
      <h2 class="heading-display fade-up" data-delay="0.06"
          style="font-size:clamp(2rem,5vw,3.2rem);margin:0 0 1.5rem;">
        Your AI works. Your organization can't absorb what it produces.
      </h2>
      <div class="card fade-up" data-delay="0.12" style="padding:2.5rem;">
        <p style="color:#a1a1aa;font-size:1rem;line-height:1.85;margin:0 0 1.25rem;">
          Decisions accelerate past governance. Knowledge fragments across tools. Context evaporates between sessions. The technology succeeds and the organization breaks.
        </p>
        <p style="color:#71717a;font-size:0.95rem;line-height:1.85;margin:0;">
          AI memory systems extract patterns from your conversations and harden them over time. If you pivot your strategy on Monday, the AI may take weeks to catch up — because its memory tends toward <strong style="color:#e4e4e7;">permanence</strong>, not <strong style="color:#e4e4e7;">persistence</strong>. The Org Brain is persistent by design. The difference is whether you govern the system or the system governs you.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<div class="divider"></div>

<!-- ── How We Work ───────────────────────────────────────────── -->
<section id="how-we-work" style="padding:5rem 0;">
  <div class="container">
    <div style="text-align:center;margin-bottom:3rem;">
      <p class="section-label fade-up" data-delay="0" style="margin-bottom:0.75rem;">How We Work</p>
      <h2 class="heading-display fade-up" data-delay="0.06"
          style="font-size:clamp(2rem,5vw,3rem);margin:0 0 1rem;">
        Three ways to build organizational intelligence.
      </h2>
      <p class="fade-up" data-delay="0.1"
         style="font-size:1rem;color:#71717a;line-height:1.75;">
        Every engagement produces a working system and a certified person to run it.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div style="display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr;gap:1.25rem;" class="services-grid">

      <!-- Done For You -->
      <div class="card fade-up" data-delay="0" style="padding:2.5rem;">
        <div style="display:flex;align-items:center;gap:0.75rem;margin-bottom:1.5rem;">
          <span class="badge">01</span>
          <span style="color:#3f3f46;font-size:0.8rem;font-family:'JetBrains Mono',monospace;">Done For You</span>
        </div>
        <h3 class="heading-upright" style="font-size:1.4rem;margin:0 0 1rem;color:#fff;">Build Your Org Brain</h3>
        <p style="color:#71717a;font-size:0.95rem;line-height:1.8;margin:0 0 1.5rem;">
          Starling builds your organizational intelligence system directly. C-suite immersion. Guided extraction. Your values, positioning, processes, and culture codified into persistent memory. Your Domain Language Model comes online.
        </p>
        <div style="padding:1rem 1.25rem;background:rgba(249,115,22,0.05);border:1px solid rgba(249,115,22,0.15);border-radius:8px;">
          <p style="font-family:'JetBrains Mono',monospace;font-size:0.72rem;color:#f97316;letter-spacing:0.05em;margin:0 0 0.3rem;text-transform:uppercase;">Deliverable</p>
          <p style="font-size:0.875rem;color:#a1a1aa;margin:0;">Working Org Brain + certified System Librarian (internal or placed)</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- License -->
      <div class="card fade-up" data-delay="0.06" style="padding:2.5rem;">
        <div style="display:flex;align-items:center;gap:0.75rem;margin-bottom:1.5rem;">
          <span class="badge">02</span>
          <span style="color:#3f3f46;font-size:0.8rem;font-family:'JetBrains Mono',monospace;">License</span>
        </div>
        <h3 class="heading-upright" style="font-size:1.4rem;margin:0 0 1rem;color:#fff;">Cognitive Design Program</h3>
        <p style="color:#71717a;font-size:0.95rem;line-height:1.8;margin:0 0 1.5rem;">
          License the methodology to run at scale inside your organization, your accelerator, or your consulting practice. We train your trainers. You certify your people. The curriculum and installers are yours to deploy.
        </p>
        <div style="padding:1rem 1.25rem;background:rgba(249,115,22,0.05);border:1px solid rgba(249,115,22,0.15);border-radius:8px;">
          <p style="font-family:'JetBrains Mono',monospace;font-size:0.72rem;color:#f97316;letter-spacing:0.05em;margin:0 0 0.3rem;text-transform:uppercase;">Deliverable</p>
          <p style="font-size:0.875rem;color:#a1a1aa;margin:0;">Per-cohort license + certified facilitators who deliver the program internally</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Every Gate -->
      <div class="card fade-up" data-delay="0.12" style="padding:2.5rem;">
        <div style="display:flex;align-items:center;gap:0.75rem;margin-bottom:1.5rem;">
          <span class="badge">03</span>
          <span style="color:#3f3f46;font-size:0.8rem;font-family:'JetBrains Mono',monospace;">Every Gate</span>
        </div>
        <h3 class="heading-upright" style="font-size:1.4rem;margin:0 0 1rem;color:#fff;">Certify or Place</h3>
        <p style="color:#71717a;font-size:0.95rem;line-height:1.8;margin:0 0 1.5rem;">
          At the end of every engagement, your organization gets a person — either trained from within or placed from the Starling network. You don't just get a methodology. You get the human who runs it.
        </p>
        <div style="padding:1rem 1.25rem;background:rgba(249,115,22,0.05);border:1px solid rgba(249,115,22,0.15);border-radius:8px;">
          <p style="font-family:'JetBrains Mono',monospace;font-size:0.72rem;color:#f97316;letter-spacing:0.05em;margin:0 0 0.3rem;text-transform:uppercase;">Deliverable</p>
          <p style="font-size:0.875rem;color:#a1a1aa;margin:0;">System Librarian, Cognitive Designer, or Chief Intelligence Officer — yours to keep</p>
        </div>
      </div>

    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<div class="divider"></div>

<!-- ── The Curriculum ─────────────────────────────────────────── -->
<section style="padding:5rem 0;">
  <div class="container">
    <div style="text-align:center;margin-bottom:3rem;">
      <p class="section-label fade-up" data-delay="0" style="margin-bottom:0.75rem;">The Curriculum</p>
      <h2 class="heading-display fade-up" data-delay="0.06"
          style="font-size:clamp(2rem,5vw,3rem);margin:0 0 1rem;">
        Eight sprints. Three certifications.
      </h2>
      <p class="fade-up" data-delay="0.1"
         style="font-size:1rem;color:#71717a;line-height:1.75;max-width:600px;margin-inline:auto;">
        The Cognitive Design Accelerator takes an organization from zero to full organizational intelligence — codified, connected, and governed. Each certification gate is a natural stopping point with a complete deliverable.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div style="display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:1.5rem;max-width:900px;margin-inline:auto;">

      <!-- Track 1 -->
      <div class="card fade-up" data-delay="0" style="padding:0;overflow:hidden;">
        <div style="padding:1.5rem 2rem;background:rgba(249,115,22,0.06);border-bottom:1px solid rgba(249,115,22,0.15);">
          <div style="display:flex;align-items:center;gap:1rem;flex-wrap:wrap;">
            <span class="badge">System Librarian</span>
            <span style="font-family:'JetBrains Mono',monospace;font-size:0.7rem;color:#52525b;">Sprints 1–2 · 9 weeks</span>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div style="display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr;gap:0;" class="sprint-grid">
          {[
            ['Sprint 1', 'Innovation System', 'Identity, Market, Innovation, Brand. The First Fifteen Constitutional Memories — your values, market position, product strategy, and brand voice.'],
            ['Sprint 2', 'Applied Intelligence', 'Deep strategy, active project architecture, organizational learning. Your Org Brain goes from repository to working system.'],
          ].map(([label, title, body], i) => (
            <div style={`padding:1.75rem 2rem;${i < 1 ? 'border-bottom:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.05);' : ''}`}>
              <p style="font-family:'JetBrains Mono',monospace;font-size:0.7rem;color:#52525b;margin:0 0 0.5rem;text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:0.08em;">{label}</p>
              <h4 style="font-size:1rem;color:#e4e4e7;margin:0 0 0.5rem;font-weight:600;">{title}</h4>
              <p style="font-size:0.875rem;color:#71717a;line-height:1.7;margin:0;">{body}</p>
            </div>
          ))}
        </div>

        <div style="padding:1.25rem 2rem;background:rgba(249,115,22,0.04);border-top:1px solid rgba(249,115,22,0.1);">
          <p style="font-size:0.875rem;color:#a1a1aa;margin:0;"><span style="color:#f97316;">☆ Gate:</span> Build and govern an Org Brain. For most startups and mid-market companies, this is the complete package.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Track 2 -->
      <div class="card fade-up" data-delay="0.06" style="padding:0;overflow:hidden;">
        <div style="padding:1.5rem 2rem;background:rgba(249,115,22,0.06);border-bottom:1px solid rgba(249,115,22,0.15);">
          <div style="display:flex;align-items:center;gap:1rem;flex-wrap:wrap;">
            <span class="badge">Cognitive Designer</span>
            <span style="font-family:'JetBrains Mono',monospace;font-size:0.7rem;color:#52525b;">Sprints 3–5 · 12 weeks</span>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div style="display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr;gap:0;" class="sprint-grid">
          {[
            ['Sprint 3', 'Optimization System', 'Productivity, Workflow, Process, Culture. How decisions get made and how work flows.'],
            ['Sprint 4', 'Cognitive System', 'System configuration, dual metrics, full Org Brain activation. All 28 Constitutional Memories complete.'],
            ['Sprint 5', 'Translation System', 'Connect your Org Brain to enterprise systems. SAP, Salesforce, Workday, and 250+ integrations.'],
          ].map(([label, title, body], i) => (
            <div style={`padding:1.75rem 2rem;${i < 2 ? 'border-bottom:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.05);' : ''}`}>
              <p style="font-family:'JetBrains Mono',monospace;font-size:0.7rem;color:#52525b;margin:0 0 0.5rem;text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:0.08em;">{label}</p>
              <h4 style="font-size:1rem;color:#e4e4e7;margin:0 0 0.5rem;font-weight:600;">{title}</h4>
              <p style="font-size:0.875rem;color:#71717a;line-height:1.7;margin:0;">{body}</p>
            </div>
          ))}
        </div>

        <div style="padding:1.25rem 2rem;background:rgba(249,115,22,0.04);border-top:1px solid rgba(249,115,22,0.1);">
          <p style="font-size:0.875rem;color:#a1a1aa;margin:0;"><span style="color:#f97316;">☆ Gate:</span> Design how an organization thinks. Build systems that compound. Connect knowledge to enterprise infrastructure.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Track 3 -->
      <div class="card fade-up" data-delay="0.12" style="padding:0;overflow:hidden;">
        <div style="padding:1.5rem 2rem;background:rgba(249,115,22,0.06);border-bottom:1px solid rgba(249,115,22,0.15);">
          <div style="display:flex;align-items:center;gap:1rem;flex-wrap:wrap;">
            <span class="badge">Chief Intelligence Officer</span>
            <span style="font-family:'JetBrains Mono',monospace;font-size:0.7rem;color:#52525b;">Sprints 6–8 · 8 weeks</span>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div style="display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr;gap:0;" class="sprint-grid">
          {[
            ['Sprint 6', 'Starling OS', 'Operating prompt design, architecture, constitutional memory, governance, semantic addressing.'],
            ['Sprint 7', 'Org Strategy', 'Buy-in, deployment, executive communication. Leading intelligence as a C-suite function.'],
            ['Sprint 8', 'Governance & Impact', 'AI governance, social impact, the certification economy, and the responsibility framework.'],
          ].map(([label, title, body], i) => (
            <div style={`padding:1.75rem 2rem;${i < 2 ? 'border-bottom:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.05);' : ''}`}>
              <p style="font-family:'JetBrains Mono',monospace;font-size:0.7rem;color:#52525b;margin:0 0 0.5rem;text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:0.08em;">{label}</p>
              <h4 style="font-size:1rem;color:#e4e4e7;margin:0 0 0.5rem;font-weight:600;">{title}</h4>
              <p style="font-size:0.875rem;color:#71717a;line-height:1.7;margin:0;">{body}</p>
            </div>
          ))}
        </div>

        <div style="padding:1.25rem 2rem;background:rgba(249,115,22,0.04);border-top:1px solid rgba(249,115,22,0.1);">
          <p style="font-size:0.875rem;color:#a1a1aa;margin:0;"><span style="color:#f97316;">☆ Gate:</span> Architect, deploy, and govern enterprise-wide organizational intelligence responsibly. The C-suite function.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

    </div>

    <div style="text-align:center;margin-top:2rem;" class="fade-up" data-delay="0.2">
      <a href="/cognitive-design" class="btn btn-ghost">Explore the Full Curriculum →</a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<div class="divider"></div>

<!-- ── Corporate Licensing ────────────────────────────────────── -->
<section style="padding:5rem 0;">
  <div class="container">
    <div style="text-align:center;margin-bottom:3rem;">
      <p class="section-label fade-up" data-delay="0" style="margin-bottom:0.75rem;">Corporate Licensing</p>
      <h2 class="heading-display fade-up" data-delay="0.06"
          style="font-size:clamp(2rem,5vw,3rem);margin:0 0 1rem;">
        License the methodology.<br/>Train your people. Scale without us.
      </h2>
      <p class="fade-up" data-delay="0.1"
         style="font-size:1rem;color:#71717a;line-height:1.75;max-width:540px;margin-inline:auto;">
        Per-cohort licensing for organizations that need Cognitive Design at workforce scale. We deliver the first cohort directly. Your certified facilitators deliver every cohort after.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div style="overflow-x:auto;" class="fade-up" data-delay="0.14">
      <table class="ptable" style="min-width:680px;">
        <thead>
          <tr>
            <th></th>
            <th>Sprint License</th>
            <th>Program License</th>
            <th>Enterprise License</th>
          </tr>
        </thead>
        <tbody>
          {[
            ['Curriculum', 'Sprints 1–2', 'Sprints 3–5', 'Sprints 6–8'],
            ['Certification', 'System Librarian', 'Cognitive Designer', 'Chief Intelligence Officer'],
            ['Cohort Size', '15–25 participants', '8–15 participants', '3–8 participants'],
            ['Duration', '9 weeks', '12 weeks', '8 weeks'],
            ['Cohort License', '$25,000', '$50,000', '$75,000'],
            ['Per-Seat Certification', '$500', '$1,500', '$5,000'],
          ].map(([feat, a, b, c]) => (
            <tr>
              <td>{feat}</td>
              <td>{a}</td>
              <td>{b}</td>
              <td>{c}</td>
            </tr>
          ))}
          <tr>
            <td>Includes</td>
            <td style="font-size:0.8rem;color:#71717a;line-height:1.6;">iPub library, installer frameworks, facilitator guides, SY12 diagnostic, Starling support</td>
            <td style="font-size:0.8rem;color:#71717a;line-height:1.6;">Everything in Sprint + train-the-trainer delivery, advanced diagnostics</td>
            <td style="font-size:0.8rem;color:#71717a;line-height:1.6;">Everything in Program + OS customization, governance architecture</td>
          </tr>
        </tbody>
      </table>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<div class="divider"></div>

<!-- ── Who This Is For ────────────────────────────────────────── -->
<section style="padding:5rem 0;">
  <div class="container">
    <div style="text-align:center;margin-bottom:3rem;">
      <p class="section-label fade-up" data-delay="0" style="margin-bottom:0.75rem;">Who This Is For</p>
      <h2 class="heading-display fade-up" data-delay="0.06"
          style="font-size:clamp(2rem,5vw,3rem);margin:0;">
        Three markets. One methodology.
      </h2>
    </div>

    <div style="display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr;gap:1.25rem;" class="markets-grid">

      <div class="card fade-up" data-delay="0" style="padding:2rem;">
        <div style="display:flex;align-items:center;gap:0.75rem;margin-bottom:0.5rem;">
          <span class="badge">Enterprise</span>
        </div>
        <p style="font-family:'JetBrains Mono',monospace;font-size:0.68rem;color:#52525b;margin:0 0 1rem;text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:0.08em;">CHRO · CIO · VP AI Strategy</p>
        <p style="color:#71717a;font-size:0.9rem;line-height:1.75;margin:0 0 1rem;">
          Organizations deploying AI at scale who need structured knowledge architecture, not just more tools. Train 20 or 2,000.
        </p>
        <p style="font-size:0.825rem;color:#52525b;line-height:1.7;margin:0;">
          <strong style="color:#a1a1aa;">Model:</strong> Sprint License pilot → Program License for facilitator corps → Enterprise License for leadership. Self-sustaining within two quarters.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="card fade-up" data-delay="0.06" style="padding:2rem;">
        <div style="display:flex;align-items:center;gap:0.75rem;margin-bottom:0.5rem;">
          <span class="badge">Accelerators</span>
        </div>
        <p style="font-family:'JetBrains Mono',monospace;font-size:0.68rem;color:#52525b;margin:0 0 1rem;text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:0.08em;">Program Director · Managing Partner</p>
        <p style="color:#71717a;font-size:0.9rem;line-height:1.75;margin:0 0 1rem;">
          Give every startup in your batch a working Org Brain by demo day. Their AI produces strategically coherent output — not generic decks.
        </p>
        <p style="font-size:0.825rem;color:#52525b;line-height:1.7;margin:0;">
          <strong style="color:#a1a1aa;">Model:</strong> Sprint License per batch. Each startup leaves with a working DLM, a certified System Librarian, and a Starling Workspace account.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="card fade-up" data-delay="0.12" style="padding:2rem;">
        <div style="display:flex;align-items:center;gap:0.75rem;margin-bottom:0.5rem;">
          <span class="badge">Consulting Firms</span>
        </div>
        <p style="font-family:'JetBrains Mono',monospace;font-size:0.68rem;color:#52525b;margin:0 0 1rem;text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:0.08em;">Practice Lead · MD of AI/Digital</p>
        <p style="color:#71717a;font-size:0.9rem;line-height:1.75;margin:0 0 1rem;">
          Add organizational intelligence to your AI transformation practice. Certify your consultants. Deliver Org Brain builds to your clients under your brand.
        </p>
        <p style="font-size:0.825rem;color:#52525b;line-height:1.7;margin:0;">
          <strong style="color:#a1a1aa;">Model:</strong> Program License to certify consultants → consultants deliver Sprint License engagements to clients. 3–6× markup on Starling's cost.
        </p>
      </div>

    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<div class="divider"></div>

<!-- ── Exit Guarantee ─────────────────────────────────────────── -->
<section style="padding:5rem 0;">
  <div class="container">
    <div style="max-width:820px;margin-inline:auto;">
      <p class="section-label fade-up" data-delay="0" style="margin-bottom:0.75rem;text-align:center;">The Exit Guarantee</p>
      <h2 class="heading-display fade-up" data-delay="0.06"
          style="font-size:clamp(2rem,5vw,3rem);margin:0 0 1rem;text-align:center;">
        Every engagement ends with a person.
      </h2>
      <p class="fade-up" data-delay="0.1"
         style="font-size:1rem;color:#71717a;line-height:1.75;text-align:center;margin-bottom:2.5rem;">
        At every certification gate, you have two options. Either way, your organization gets the human capability to sustain what was built.
      </p>

      <div style="display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr;gap:1.25rem;" class="guarantee-grid">

        <div class="card fade-up" data-delay="0.12" style="padding:2rem;">
          <div style="display:flex;align-items:center;gap:0.75rem;margin-bottom:1.25rem;">
            <span class="badge">Option A</span>
          </div>
          <h3 style="font-size:1.1rem;color:#fff;margin:0 0 0.75rem;">Certify someone inside your org.</h3>
          <p style="color:#71717a;font-size:0.9rem;line-height:1.75;margin:0 0 1.25rem;">
            An internal employee earns the credential through demonstrated mastery — not attendance. They own the knowledge, the tools, and the ongoing governance.
          </p>
          <div style="display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:0.4rem;">
            {[
              ['System Librarian', '$65–$85K'],
              ['Cognitive Designer', '$95–$120K'],
              ['Chief Intelligence Officer', '$150–$200K+'],
            ].map(([role, comp]) => (
              <div style="display:flex;justify-content:space-between;align-items:center;padding:0.5rem 0;border-bottom:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.05);">
                <span style="font-size:0.875rem;color:#a1a1aa;">{role}</span>
                <span style="font-family:'JetBrains Mono',monospace;font-size:0.8rem;color:#f97316;">{comp}</span>
              </div>
            ))}
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="card fade-up" data-delay="0.16" style="padding:2rem;">
          <div style="display:flex;align-items:center;gap:0.75rem;margin-bottom:1.25rem;">
            <span class="badge">Option B</span>
          </div>
          <h3 style="font-size:1.1rem;color:#fff;margin:0 0 0.75rem;">We place someone from our network.</h3>
          <p style="color:#71717a;font-size:0.9rem;line-height:1.75;margin:0 0 1.25rem;">
            Starling places a pre-certified professional from the broader talent network. Same credentials, same capability — ready to operate from day one.
          </p>
          <div style="display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:0.4rem;">
            {[
              ['System Librarian', '$65–$85K'],
              ['Cognitive Designer', '$95–$120K'],
              ['Chief Intelligence Officer', '$150–$200K+'],
            ].map(([role, comp]) => (
